&lt;p&gt;The cuisine of Mark Best is inventive and progressive which earned his restaurant Marque &lt;strong&gt;Elite Traveler Magazine&rsquo;s Elite 100 Restaurants #35 &lt;/strong&gt;and&lt;strong&gt; Gourmet Traveler magazine&rsquo;s #3 spot on its 2014 Top 100 Restaurants &lt;/strong&gt;list&nbsp;in Australia. The room is modern black and white with lighting that bathes guests in a warm glow. Attire is smart casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please &lt;a title=&quot;Marque Restaurant Reservations&quot; href=&quot;http://marquerestaurant.com.au/reservations/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;book online&lt;/a&gt; or, preferably, contact Marque by phone at +61 2 9332 2225 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:dine@marquerestaurant.com.au&quot;&gt;dine@marquerestaurant.com.au&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Reservations must be reconfirmed. Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 48 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. If the reservation is not reconfirmed the table may be given away. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
